item.title: Privacy Policy for FotoGenius App
item.description: Introduction Welcome to the Privacy Policy for FotoGenius. Your privacy is critically important to us. This Privacy Policy aims to give you information on how we collect and process your personal data through the usage of our app, FotoGenius. Data We Collect What data does your app collect? Our app collects images and text inputs that you voluntarily provide. These may include faces for our face-swapping features, as well as other images and text for our image-to-image and text-to-image machine learning algorithms.
